title: [P3D] ORBX FTXEUGENv1.20RIP
description:
copy the contents of this folder into your :simroot folder
there may be over writes for the texture files so just compare them with your existing files and choose the most up to date ones

This RIP will show in your FTX CENTRAL as installed and up to date and FTX CENTRAL will config it

if you don't use FTX CENTRAL then your probably able to activate it using LORBY-SI AddonOrginizer anyway

for ORBX stuff i use the OFFLINE FTX CENTRAL version 3.2.2.8 downloaded from PB
im hoping someone will come up with a later version of the OFFLINE FTX CENTRAL since the above doesn't show GES even though i have it downloaded and installed from rutacker.org

this RIP is made from the P3Dv3 installer with updates to P3Dv4 available @

this RIP works fine for me with P3D v4.2 and GES installed first since it was availavle as a RIP @

if anyone finds anything missing let me know i'll try to fix it

i cannot seed 24/7 so i'll do UTC 23:00 to 08:00 or there abouts
